description: Try our fragrant and sumptuous Thai Red Curry Paste. Traditionally prepared with dried red chillies, this dish is a sweeter and milder curry, perfectly balanced with the sourness of kaffir lime and the savoury notes of shallot and garlic. Red curry dishes are widely enjoyed throughout Thailand.
name: Thai Red Curry Paste
